      "author": "j4ckofalltrades",
      "description": "# 0.1.0 (initial release)\r\n\r\nDisplays numbered badges (1-8) on Obsidian tabs when Ctrl or Cmd is held. When working with split panes, each split will have its own tab sequence and tab numbers will only be displayed on the currently active (split) pane.\r\n\r\nThis plugin complements the default Obsidian keyboard shortcuts for switching tabs (Ctrl/Cmd 1-8, 9 selects the last tab) by adding tab number 'hints'.",
